# Examenes API
@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000
@authToken = {{authToken}}

## Rutas publicas

### Crear examen (publico)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/examen/public
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "HB001",
  "name": "Hemograma",
  "method": "Automatizado",
  "specimenType": "SANGRE",
  "processingTimeMin": 60,
  "priceBase": 25.0,
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### Listar examenes (publico)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/examenes/public
Accept: application/json

### Obtener examen por id (publico)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/examen/1/public
Accept: application/json

### Actualizar examen (publico)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/examen/1/public
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "method": "Manual",
  "processingTimeMin": 75,
  "priceBase": 28.5,
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### Eliminar examen fisicamente (publico)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/examen/1/public

### Baja logica de examen (publico)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/examen/1/logic/public
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "INACTIVE"
}

## Rutas protegidas (requieren token)

### Crear examen (con auth)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/examen
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "GLU001",
  "name": "Glucosa en sangre",
  "method": "Enzimatico",
  "specimenType": "SANGRE",
  "processingTimeMin": 45,
  "priceBase": 18.0,
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### Listar examenes (con auth)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/examenes
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Obtener examen por id (con auth)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/examen/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Actualizar examen (con auth)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/examen/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "method": "Automatizado",
  "processingTimeMin": 50,
  "priceBase": 20.0,
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### Eliminar examen fisicamente (con auth)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/examen/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Baja logica de examen (con auth)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/examen/1/logic
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "INACTIVE"
}
